[[rbtgo_lode_underpin]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_lode_underpin}

Captures a vendor-published WSL rootfs into a single {rbtga_lode}
({rbtgog_lode}),
fetching the tarball cloud-side into one `{gar_lodes_namespace}/` package under a host-minted {rbtga_touchmark}.
The {rbtr_director} submits a two-step Cloud Build job — curl fetch with GPG-verified published-checksum verification and opaque-blob wrap, then a vouch push — writing the {rbtga_lode_vouch} provenance envelope to its one canonical home, the `:rbi_vouch` tag in GAR, and handing the touchmark forward host-side as the {rbf_fact_lode}.
The wsl kind is the structural outlier: its upstream is an HTTPS tarball plus an out-of-band signed checksum, not an OCI image, so its capture step is new — and intent is declarative (version arguments, no FQIN), with the checksum discovered and signature-verified at capture.

include::RBSLU-lode_underpin.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_lode_divine]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_lode_divine}

Enumerates every {rbtga_lode} under the `{gar_lodes_namespace}/` namespace
({rbtgog_lode}),
reading each {rbtga_touchmark} and its glance fingerprint.
Read-only and kind-agnostic — the kind is decoded from the touchmark's leading letter.

include::RBSLD-lode_divine.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_lode_augur]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_lode_augur}

Augurs a single {rbtga_lode} — inspecting its member tags and decoding its {rbtga_lode_vouch}
({rbtgog_lode}).
Read-only and kind-agnostic; the single-Lode inspect counterpart to {rbtgo_lode_divine} enumeration, paralleling made-side {rbtgo_ark_inspect}.

include::RBSLA-lode_augur.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_lode_banish]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_lode_banish}

Banishes a whole {rbtga_lode}
({rbtgog_lode})
via a single GAR `packages delete` on the touchmark package — the atomic whole-Lode delete.
Kind-agnostic; parallels made-side {rbtgo_ark_abjure}.

include::RBSLB-lode_banish.adoc[]

[[mkr_command_exec]]
//axvo_procedure axd_transient axd_internal
=== {mkr_command_exec}

include::RBSCE-command_exec.adoc[]

